ess in the flagship market;\nWork with the BPC Corporate team to report on the progress of initiatives;\nPartner with Marketing and Events to develop a strategy plan for the flagship market.', null, null, 0, 221004, '20161101000000999000000001', '°××ÓÑÀ', to_date('01-03-2017 11:55:16', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), 0, null, '0', 0, null, null, null);
