        'Responsibilities:\nClient and Business Development:\nWork with BPC Head of Region to design the BPC strategy in the region and lead BPC Managers to execute this;\nIdentify methods of generating new business in the stores and increasing VIC sales;\nProactively network to develop new business opportunities within the region e.g. Corporations, Concierge groups, etc.;\nPartner with Store Managers to produce a development plan for BPC, e.g. event and strategy planning, strategic positioning, calendar sharing, budget proposals;\nCollaborate with Marketing & Events to generate new business opportunities and partnerships.\nTeam Development:\nEquip, coach, and motivate the team to deliver the sales targets for the region;\nRoll out BPC initiatives to the team as directed by the Head of Region;\nTrack progress and drive results with BPC Managers and Store Managers on a monthly basis;\nEnsure Managers are driving the right behaviours and that their teams are adhering to associated policies and consistently delivering the Burberry Experience to clients;\nWork with BPC Managers on the recruitment of BPC Consultants by partnering with Store Managers and Regional Directors.\nReporting/Feedback:\nMonitor regional BPC performance with the Regional Directors and the BPC HoR by reviewing and communicating progress and evaluating results against the region¡¯s annual plan;\nPartner with BPC Managers and Store Managers to review weekly customer reports and identify opportunities;\nMonitor and report on regional events and networking and evaluate effectiveness of strategy and approach;\nShare best practices by communicating regularly with BPC Global team.\nInternal Relationship Management:\nReport to the Head of Region on strategy and team progress and development and provide insight and recommendations to the HoR/Corporate team;\nWork collaboratively with BPC Managers to ensure Consultants objectives are set, measured and achieved and to drive growth and cultivation of VIC business in the flagship market;\nWork with the BPC Corporate team to report on the progress of initiatives;\nPartner with Marketing and Events to develop a strategy plan for the flagship market.', null, null, 0, '221004', '20161101000000999000000001', '°××ÓÑÀ', to_date('01-03-2017 11:55:16', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), 0, null, '0', 0, null, null, null);
