ationships with landlords and developers;\nMonitor the counterfeits and parallel trade activities in the local market, report them to the Brand Protection Manager and Legal Department and to assist them in the following up of these issues.', null, null, 0, '221005', '20161101000000999000000001', '°××ÓÑÀ', to_date('01-03-2017 11:55:16', 'dd-mm-yyyy hh24:mi:ss'), 0, null, '0', 0, null, null, null);
