 training program for new staffs;\nDeveloped TH DNA customer service missions and standards to ensure consistent perceived value by customers from all boutiques;\nManage relationship with landlords and local government officials;\nDeep involved in boutique design work together with HQ and design company;\nWork with local contractors for boutique constructions for project management;\nWork with marketing department for developing retail marketing calendar with various activities such as boutique visual plans, holiday animation plans, VIP programs;\nInitiate and conduct the coaching program for franchised boutiques.\n\nAchievements:\nSuccessfully opened 6 direct-run TH boutiques in China with global concept;\nSuccessfully launched TH luxury mobile phone and TH lifestyle products in China direct-run boutiques;\nTotal sales performance of Retail in 2011 account for 25% of total TH China watch net sales and 56% of total TH China mobile phone net sales;\nBeijing SKP TH boutique ranked No.1 in all TH Asia Pacific boutiques by sell-out/ sqm in 2010 and created highest daily sell-out record of 500K;\nStable team with low staff turnover of 10%;\nNo product lose case in all boutiques.', 
